'''馬哈拉施特拉節'''（[[馬拉提語|馬拉提語]]：महाराष्ट्र दिन）是一個訂定在每年[[5月1日|5月1日]]的[[馬哈拉施特拉邦|馬哈拉施特拉邦]]邦定節日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.officeholidays.com/countries/india/maharashtra/2014.php|title=Public Holidays in Maharashtra in 2014|publisher=OfficeHolidays|accessdate=2016-05-27|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928005622/http://www.officeholidays.com/countries/india/maharashtra/2014.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目的是為了紀念馬哈拉施特拉邦的建立<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.maharashtratourism.net/festivals/maharashtra-day.html |title = Maharashtra Day |publisher = Maharashtra Tourism |accessdate = 2016-05-27 |archive-date = 2015-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150502182814/http://www.maharashtratourism.net/festivals/maharashtra-day.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==背景==
1956年時，政府決定根據人民的使用語言重新劃分行政區塊<ref>{{cite web|title=THE STATES REORGANISATION ACT, 1956|url=http://www.indiankanoon.org/doc/1211891/|publisher=[[印度政府|印度政府]]|accessdate=2012-12-06|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519225002/https://indiankanoon.org/doc/1211891/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[印度議會|印度議會]]於1960年4月25日通過了該改革法案，並於5月1日生效<ref>{{cite web|title=THE BOMBAY RE-ORGANISATION ACT, 1960 No.11 OF 1960|url=http://www.legalhelpindia.com/bareacts/THE%20BOMBAY%20RE-ORGANISATION%20ACT,%201960%20No.11%20OF%201960.doc|publisher=[[印度政府|印度政府]]|accessdate=2012-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111203075507/http://www.legalhelpindia.com/bareacts/THE%20BOMBAY%20RE-ORGANISATION%20ACT,%201960%20No.11%20OF%201960.doc|archive-date=2011-12-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，為了紀念這個重大的改革而設立此節日。

==紀念活動==
2011年為馬哈拉施特拉邦建立50周年的日子，因此在全馬哈拉施特拉邦特別進行了金禧慶祝活動<ref>{{cite web | title=Maharashtra's golden jubilee grand finale on Monday | url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-04-30/mumbai/29490594_1_finale-jubilee-celebrations | publisher=[[印度時報|印度時報]] | accessdate=2012-12-06 | archive-date=2013-01-26 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20130126053445/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-04-30/mumbai/29490594_1_finale-jubilee-celebrations | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Maharashtra: Political parties gear up for a grand golden jubilee day | url=http://news.rediff.com/report/2010/apr/29/how-maha-will-celebrate-its-golden-jubilee-day.htm | publisher=rediff.com | accessdate=2012-12-06 | archive-date=2016-06-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624041339/http://news.rediff.com/report/2010/apr/29/how-maha-will-celebrate-its-golden-jubilee-day.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

